I’m confused. It’s enabled, which means code must be running. Try popping up a larger log window on the right hand side (via the gear icon) to see more log information–this console should also be visible in the riolog window in vscode.

The “internal issue with print and error tags” is fixed in more recent DS updates (patch 2 was recently released).
